  "description": "<p>Extends from Charleston, West Virginia in the east to Ironton, Ohio in the west. Main cities include Charleston and Huntington in West Virginia, Ashland in Kentucky, and Ironton in Ohio.</p>\n<p>Made using the Map Patcher by Kronifer and US Demand Generator by slurry.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>Airports: WV International Yeager Airport (CRW), Huntington Tri-State Airport (HTS)</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Universities: Marshall University, West Virginia State University, University of Charleston, BridgeValley Community and Technical College, Ashland Community and Technical College, Ohio University Southern</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Entertainment/Tourism: West Virginia Capitol, Joan C. Edwards Stadium, University of Charleston Stadium, Charleston, Huntington, and Ashland Malls</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Note: The name of the city in game is just Huntington since Charleston-Huntington was too long and Charleston is also a city in South Carolina</p>",
